<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Such a Beautiful Artificial Flower"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="斯く美しき造花"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="绚美如斯之造花"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Isekaijoucho"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="ヰ世界情緒"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="异世界情绪"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Creation"/><amll:meta key="album" value="創生"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="JPZ922015554"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="1907751317"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="001pGP4X1dOiWa"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="336304143"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="7wPcxTtiu0Wnj5V9sSeMtx"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1688353216"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="174598250"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ASyunagi"/></metadata></head><body dur="3:12.540"><div begin="13.050" end="3:12.540"><p begin="13.050" end="16.460" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="13.050" end="13.540">仇</span><span begin="13.540" end="14.460">花</span><span begin="14.460" end="14.900">は</span><span begin="14.900" end="15.600">心</span><span begin="15.600" end="15.820">の</span><span begin="15.820" end="16.260">奥</span><span begin="16.260" end="16.460">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">怨念之花深藏心底</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">怨念之花深藏心底</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A barren flower deep in my heart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">헛된 꽃은 마음속 깊은 곳에</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La fleur stérile au fond de mon cœur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La flor estéril en el fondo de mi corazón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Scheinblüte tief im Herzen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A flor estéril no fundo do coração</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пустоцвет в глубине сердца</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Un fiore sterile nel profondo del cuore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Adabana wa kokoro no oku ni</span></p><p begin="16.690" end="20.080" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="16.690" end="16.890">気</span><span begin="16.890" end="17.160">付</span><span begin="17.160" end="17.550">か</span><span begin="17.550" end="17.860">れ</span><span begin="17.860" end="18.050">て</span><span begin="18.050" end="18.780">終</span><span begin="18.780" end="19.010">わ</span><span begin="19.010" end="19.340">な</span><span begin="19.340" end="19.660">い</span><span begin="19.660" end="19.790">よ</span><span begin="19.790" end="19.910">う</span><span begin="19.910" end="20.080">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">唯恐被窥见而凋零</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">唯恐被窺見而凋零</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">So that it won&apos;t end by being noticed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">들켜서 끝나버리지 않도록</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pour ne pas qu&apos;on la remarque et qu&apos;elle prenne fin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Para que no acabe al ser descubierta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Damit sie nicht entdeckt wird und endet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Para que não acabe sendo notada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Чтобы всё не кончилось если его заметят</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Affinché non finisca venendo scoperto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kizukarete shimawanai you ni</span></p><p begin="20.350" end="27.080" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="20.350" end="20.830">誰</span><span begin="20.830" end="21.270">よ</span><span begin="21.270" end="21.710">り</span><span begin="21.710" end="22.170">も</span><span begin="22.170" end="22.410">無</span><span begin="22.410" end="22.650">機</span><span begin="22.650" end="23.090">質</span><span begin="23.090" end="23.320">で</span><span begin="23.320" end="23.530">あ</span><span begin="23.530" end="23.780">り</span> <span begin="23.990" end="24.800">美</span><span begin="24.800" end="25.300">し</span><span begin="25.300" end="25.790">く</span><span begin="25.790" end="26.230">あ</span><span begin="26.230" end="27.080">れ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">愿比万物更冰冷 更绮丽</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">願比萬物更冰冷 更綺麗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Be more inorganic and beautiful than anyone else</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">누구보다도 무기질적이며 아름답기를</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Sois plus inorganique et plus belle que quiconque</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sé más inorgánica que nadie y sé hermosa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sei lebloser und schöner als jeder andere</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que eu seja mais inorgânica e bela do que ninguém</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Будь безжизненнее и прекраснее всех</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sii più inorganica di chiunque altro e sii bella</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dare yori mo mukishitsu de ari utsukushiku are</span></p><p begin="27.370" end="31.040" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="27.370" end="27.870">壊</span><span begin="27.870" end="28.070">れ</span><span begin="28.070" end="28.410">な</span><span begin="28.410" end="28.780">い</span><span begin="28.780" end="28.960">理</span><span begin="28.960" end="29.460">想</span><span begin="29.460" end="29.680">を</span><span begin="29.680" end="30.220">描</span><span begin="30.220" end="30.590">く</span><span begin="30.590" end="30.810">と</span><span begin="30.810" end="31.040">き</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">描绘永不崩坏的理想时</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">描繪永不崩壞的理想時</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">When painting an unbreakable ideal</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">부서지지 않는 이상을 그릴 때</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quand je dessine un idéal indestructible</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cuando dibujo un ideal inquebrantable</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn man ein unzerbrechliches Ideal zeichnet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ao desenhar um ideal inquebrável</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Когда я рисую нерушимый идеал</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quando disegno un ideale indistruttibile</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kowarenai risou o egaku toki</span></p><p begin="31.270" end="34.870" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="31.270" end="31.720">誰</span><span begin="31.720" end="32.080">か</span><span begin="32.080" end="32.410">の</span><span begin="32.410" end="32.810">眼</span><span begin="32.810" end="33.030">差</span><span begin="33.030" end="33.320">し</span><span begin="33.320" end="33.550">を</span><span begin="33.550" end="34.390">瞞</span><span begin="34.390" end="34.870">す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">欺骗着某人的视线</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">欺騙著某人的視線</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Deceive someone&apos;s gaze</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">누군가의 시선을 속여 넘겨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je trompe le regard de quelqu&apos;un</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Engaño la mirada de alguien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Täuscht man den Blick von jemandem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Engano o olhar de alguém</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">То обманываю чей-то взгляд</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Inganno lo sguardo di qualcuno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dareka no manazashi o mayakasu</span></p><p begin="35.340" end="38.290" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="35.340" end="36.040">嫋</span><span begin="36.040" end="36.230">や</span><span begin="36.230" end="36.500">か</span><span begin="36.500" end="36.690">な</span><span begin="36.690" end="37.200">感</span><span begin="37.200" end="37.830">情</span><span begin="37.830" end="38.090">か</span><span begin="38.090" end="38.290">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">从袅袅情愫间</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">從裊裊情愫間</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">From delicate emotions</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">가냘프고 유연한 감정에서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">De ces émotions gracieuses</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Desde estas emociones delicadas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Aus zierlichen Gefühlen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">De emoções graciosas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Из этих утончённых чувств</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Da emozioni aggraziate</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Taoyaka na kanjou kara</span></p><p begin="38.520" end="42.200" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="38.520" end="38.780">こ</span><span begin="38.780" end="38.960">の</span><span begin="38.960" end="39.690">声</span><span begin="39.690" end="39.920">は</span><span begin="39.920" end="40.820">迸</span><span begin="40.820" end="42.200">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">迸发出这声线</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">迸發出這聲線</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">This voice surges forth</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 목소리는 솟구쳐 올라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Cette voix jaillit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Brota esta voz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bricht diese Stimme hervor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Esta voz jorra</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Вырывается этот голос</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sgorga questa voce</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kono koe wa hotobashiru</span></p><p begin="42.620" end="48.400" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="42.620" end="43.030">あ</span><span begin="43.030" end="43.080">、</span><span begin="43.300" end="43.490">呼</span><span begin="43.490" end="44.210">吸</span><span begin="44.210" end="44.450">が</span><span begin="44.450" end="44.740">で</span><span begin="44.740" end="45.140">き</span><span begin="45.140" end="45.380">な</span><span begin="45.380" end="45.650">い</span><span begin="45.650" end="46.020">ま</span><span begin="46.020" end="46.260">ま</span><span begin="46.260" end="46.950">抱</span><span begin="46.950" end="47.190">え</span><span begin="47.190" end="47.520">た</span><span begin="47.520" end="48.090">痛</span><span begin="48.090" end="48.400">み</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 无法呼吸却紧拥的痛楚</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 無法呼吸卻緊擁的痛楚</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah the pain embraced while unable to breathe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아, 숨도 쉬지 못한 채 끌어안은 아픔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah la douleur que j&apos;ai portée sans pouvoir respirer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah, este dolor que abrazo sin poder respirar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah der Schmerz den ich atemlos ertrug</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah, a dor que carrego sem conseguir respirar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ах боль что я таила задыхаясь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah il dolore che ho abbracciato senza poter respirare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">A, kokyuu ga dekinai mama kakaeta itami</span></p><p begin="49.180" end="56.720" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="49.180" end="49.880">解</span><span begin="49.880" end="50.270">け</span><span begin="50.270" end="50.590">ず</span><span begin="50.590" end="50.800">に</span><span begin="50.800" end="51.480">絡</span><span begin="51.480" end="51.750">み</span><span begin="51.750" end="52.070">合</span><span begin="52.070" end="52.370">う</span><span begin="52.370" end="52.900">造</span><span begin="52.900" end="53.320">花</span><span begin="53.320" end="53.490">の</span><span begin="53.490" end="54.970">様</span><span begin="55.360" end="56.720">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">如人造花般纠缠不散</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">如人造花般糾纏不散</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Like artificial flowers entwining without coming undone</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">풀리지 않고 얽혀드는 조화처럼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Telle une fleur artificielle qui s&apos;entremêle sans se défaire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Como flores artificiales que se enredan sin poder desatarse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wie künstliche Blumen die sich unlöslich ineinander verschlingen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como flores artificiais que se emaranham sem se desfazer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Словно сплетающиеся не в силах распутаться искусственные цветы</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Come fiori artificiali che si intrecciano senza sciogliersi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hodokezu ni karamiau zouka no you ni</span></p><p begin="57.120" end="1:02.920" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="57.120" end="57.540">あ</span><span begin="57.540" end="57.590">、</span><span begin="57.860" end="58.070">何</span><span begin="58.070" end="58.480">処</span><span begin="58.480" end="58.780">へ</span><span begin="58.780" end="59.010">も</span><span begin="59.010" end="59.320">行</span><span begin="59.320" end="59.660">け</span><span begin="59.660" end="59.800">ず</span><span begin="59.800" end="1:00.310">彷</span><span begin="1:00.310" end="1:00.820">徨</span><span begin="1:00.820" end="1:01.160">え</span><span begin="1:01.160" end="1:01.500">な</span><span begin="1:01.500" end="1:01.720">い</span><span begin="1:01.720" end="1:02.180">の</span><span begin="1:02.180" end="1:02.410">な</span><span begin="1:02.410" end="1:02.640">ら</span><span begin="1:02.640" end="1:02.920">ば</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 若注定无处可去 无法彷徨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 若注定無處可去 無法彷徨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah if I can neither go anywhere nor wander</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아, 아무 데도 가지 못하고 헤맬 수조차 없다면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah si je ne peux aller nulle part ni même errer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah, si no puedo ir a ninguna parte ni vagar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah wenn ich nirgendwohin gehen und nicht umherwandern kann</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah, se não posso ir a lugar nenhum nem vagar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ах если мне некуда идти и негде блуждать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah se non posso andare da nessuna parte e non posso vagare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">A, doko e mo yukezu samayoenai no naraba</span></p><p begin="1:03.730" end="1:08.330" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:03.730" end="1:04.440">鮮</span><span begin="1:04.440" end="1:04.740">や</span><span begin="1:04.740" end="1:05.130">か</span><span begin="1:05.130" end="1:05.360">な</span><span begin="1:05.360" end="1:05.650">モ</span><span begin="1:05.650" end="1:05.990">ノ</span><span begin="1:05.990" end="1:06.260">ク</span><span begin="1:06.260" end="1:06.610">ロ</span><span begin="1:06.610" end="1:06.910">に</span><span begin="1:06.910" end="1:07.190">染</span><span begin="1:07.190" end="1:07.390">ま</span><span begin="1:07.390" end="1:07.610">っ</span><span begin="1:07.610" end="1:07.970">て</span><span begin="1:07.970" end="1:08.050">い</span><span begin="1:08.050" end="1:08.330">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">便沉溺于绚烂黑白</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">便沉溺於絢爛黑白</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I am being dyed in a vivid monochrome</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">선명한 흑백으로 물들어 가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je me teins d&apos;un monochrome éclatant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me voy tiñendo de un vívido monocromo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Färbe ich mich in ein lebhaftes Monochrom</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vou me tingindo de um monocromático vívido</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я окрашиваюсь в яркий монохром</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi tingo di un vivido bianco e nero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Azayaka na monokuro ni somatte iku</span></p><p begin="1:11.260" end="1:14.690" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:11.260" end="1:11.500">手</span><span begin="1:11.500" end="1:11.720">に</span><span begin="1:11.720" end="1:12.620">残</span><span begin="1:12.620" end="1:12.980">る</span><span begin="1:12.980" end="1:13.510">僅</span><span begin="1:13.510" end="1:13.780">か</span><span begin="1:13.780" end="1:13.970">な</span><span begin="1:13.970" end="1:14.210">香</span><span begin="1:14.210" end="1:14.450">さ</span><span begin="1:14.450" end="1:14.690">え</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">掌心残存的微香</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">掌心殘存的微香</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even if the faint fragrance remaining on my hands</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">손에 남은 희미한 향기조차</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même si le faible parfum qui reste sur mes mains</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Incluso si la tenue fragancia que queda en mis manos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Selbst wenn der schwache Duft der in den Händen bleibt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo que a leve fragrância que resta nas mãos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже едва уловимый аромат что остался на руках</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche la debole fragranza che rimane tra le mani</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Te ni nokoru wazuka na ka sae</span></p><p begin="1:14.890" end="1:18.320" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:14.890" end="1:15.700">偽</span><span begin="1:15.700" end="1:16.050">り</span><span begin="1:16.050" end="1:16.280">の</span><span begin="1:16.280" end="1:16.620">意</span><span begin="1:16.620" end="1:16.940">味</span><span begin="1:16.940" end="1:17.170">だ</span><span begin="1:17.170" end="1:17.470">と</span><span begin="1:17.470" end="1:17.840">し</span><span begin="1:17.840" end="1:18.090">て</span><span begin="1:18.090" end="1:18.320">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">纵是虚妄的隐喻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">縱是虛妄的隱喻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Holds a false meaning</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">거짓된 의미라 할지라도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">A une signification mensongère</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tiene un significado falso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eine trügerische Bedeutung hat</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Seja um significado falso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже если это лишь фальшивый смысл</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche se ha un significato falso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itsuwari no imi da to shite mo</span></p><p begin="1:18.520" end="1:25.240" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:18.520" end="1:19.330">頭</span><span begin="1:19.430" end="1:19.920">か</span><span begin="1:19.920" end="1:20.250">ら</span><span begin="1:20.250" end="1:20.800">爪</span><span begin="1:20.800" end="1:21.000">の</span><span begin="1:21.000" end="1:21.510">先</span><span begin="1:21.510" end="1:21.710">ま</span><span begin="1:21.710" end="1:21.970">で</span> <span begin="1:22.170" end="1:23.000">馨</span><span begin="1:23.000" end="1:23.480">し</span><span begin="1:23.480" end="1:23.890">く</span><span begin="1:23.890" end="1:24.460">あ</span><span begin="1:24.460" end="1:25.240">れ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">从发梢到指尖 愿永葆芬芳</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">從髮梢到指尖 願永葆芬芳</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Be fragrant from head to toe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">머리부터 발끝까지 향기롭기를</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">De la tête jusqu&apos;au bout des ongles sois parfumée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">De la cabeza a los pies sé fragante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sei duftend von Kopf bis Fuß</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Da cabeça à ponta dos dedos que eu seja perfumada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">От макушки до кончиков пальцев благоухай</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dalla testa alle dita dei piedi sii profumata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Atama kara tsume no saki made kaguwashiku are</span></p><p begin="1:37.100" end="1:42.180" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:37.100" end="1:37.620">宵</span><span begin="1:37.620" end="1:38.270">闇</span><span begin="1:38.270" end="1:38.320">、</span><span begin="1:38.320" end="1:38.780">夢</span><span begin="1:38.780" end="1:39.010">を</span><span begin="1:39.010" end="1:39.230">見</span><span begin="1:39.230" end="1:39.440">る</span> <span begin="1:39.680" end="1:39.910">時</span><span begin="1:39.910" end="1:40.370">計</span><span begin="1:40.370" end="1:40.560">の</span><span begin="1:40.560" end="1:41.040">針</span><span begin="1:41.040" end="1:41.280">と</span><span begin="1:41.280" end="1:41.500">ナ</span><span begin="1:41.500" end="1:41.680">イ</span><span begin="1:41.680" end="1:41.960">フ</span><span begin="1:41.960" end="1:42.180">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">薄暮中做梦 时针与利刃</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">薄暮中做夢 時針與利刃</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Dusk, dreaming the clock hands and the knife</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">초저녁 어둠, 꿈을 꿔 시곗바늘과 나이프는</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Crépuscule je rêve les aiguilles de l&apos;horloge et le couteau</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Anochecer, tengo un sueño las manecillas del reloj y el cuchillo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Abenddämmerung träumend Uhrzeiger und Messer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Anoitecer, sonhando os ponteiros do relógio e a faca</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В сумерках я вижу сон как стрелки часов и нож</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Crepuscolo faccio un sogno le lancette dell&apos;orologio e il coltello</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yoiyami, yume o miru tokei no hari to naifu wa</span></p><p begin="1:42.620" end="1:47.810" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:42.620" end="1:43.090">耽</span><span begin="1:43.090" end="1:43.330">美</span><span begin="1:43.330" end="1:43.720">に</span><span begin="1:43.720" end="1:44.230">踊</span><span begin="1:44.230" end="1:44.450">り</span><span begin="1:44.450" end="1:44.600">だ</span><span begin="1:44.600" end="1:44.890">す</span> <span begin="1:45.110" end="1:45.350">机</span><span begin="1:45.350" end="1:45.820">上</span><span begin="1:45.820" end="1:46.050">で</span><span begin="1:46.050" end="1:46.270">為</span><span begin="1:46.270" end="1:46.520">さ</span><span begin="1:46.520" end="1:46.730">る</span><span begin="1:46.730" end="1:47.130">遊</span><span begin="1:47.130" end="1:47.410">戯</span><span begin="1:47.410" end="1:47.810">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">耽美起舞 案头游戏</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">耽美起舞 案頭遊戲</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Start dancing aesthetically the game played on the desk</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">탐미적으로 춤추기 시작해 책상 위에서 벌어지는 유희를</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Se mettent à danser avec esthétisme le jeu qui se déroule sur le bureau</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Comienzan a bailar estéticamente el juego realizado sobre el escritorio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Beginnen ästhetisch zu tanzen das Spiel auf dem Schreibtisch</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Começam a dançar esteticamente o jogo feito sobre a mesa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Эстетично пускаются в пляс в игре разыгранной на столе</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Iniziano a danzare esteticamente il gioco sulla scrivania</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tanbi ni odoridasu kijou de nasaru yuugi o</span></p><p begin="1:48.050" end="1:53.100" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:48.050" end="1:48.460">厭</span><span begin="1:48.460" end="1:49.120">世</span><span begin="1:49.120" end="1:49.170">、</span><span begin="1:49.230" end="1:49.680">流</span><span begin="1:49.680" end="1:49.880">れ</span><span begin="1:49.880" end="1:50.140">込</span><span begin="1:50.140" end="1:50.360">む</span> <span begin="1:50.590" end="1:51.030">浮</span><span begin="1:51.030" end="1:51.280">世</span><span begin="1:51.280" end="1:51.500">に</span><span begin="1:51.500" end="1:51.690">満</span><span begin="1:51.690" end="1:51.940">ち</span><span begin="1:51.940" end="1:52.170">た</span><span begin="1:52.170" end="1:52.650">嫌</span><span begin="1:52.650" end="1:52.840">悪</span><span begin="1:52.840" end="1:53.100">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">厌世流淌 尘世满溢的憎恶</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">厭世流淌 塵世滿溢的憎惡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">World-weariness, flows in if the disgust filling the transient world</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">염세, 흘러들어와 속세에 가득 찬 혐오가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pessimisme il afflue si le dégoût dont ce monde éphémère est empli</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hastío del mundo, fluye hacia adentro la aversión que llena este mundo efímero</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Weltschmerz strömt herein wenn der Ekel der diese flüchtige Welt erfüllt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Pessimismo, flui para dentro a aversão que enche este mundo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пессимизм вливается отвращение переполняющее этот бренный мир</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Pessimismo scorre dentro il disgusto di cui è pieno questo mondo transitorio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ensei, nagarekomu ukiyo ni michita keno ga</span></p><p begin="1:53.540" end="1:58.530" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:53.540" end="1:54.010">纏</span><span begin="1:54.010" end="1:54.210">わ</span><span begin="1:54.210" end="1:54.620">り</span><span begin="1:54.620" end="1:54.870">つ</span><span begin="1:54.870" end="1:55.140">く</span><span begin="1:55.140" end="1:55.370">な</span><span begin="1:55.370" end="1:55.600">ら</span><span begin="1:55.600" end="1:55.830">ば</span> <span begin="1:56.040" end="1:56.240">気</span><span begin="1:56.240" end="1:56.610">泡</span><span begin="1:56.720" end="1:56.890">と</span><span begin="1:56.890" end="1:57.150">化</span><span begin="1:57.150" end="1:57.410">せ</span><span begin="1:57.410" end="1:57.600">ば</span><span begin="1:57.600" end="1:57.850">良</span><span begin="1:57.850" end="1:58.100">い</span><span begin="1:58.100" end="1:58.320">の</span><span begin="1:58.320" end="1:58.530">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">若终将缠绕 不如化作气泡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">若終將纏繞 不如化作氣泡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Clings to me I wish it would just turn into bubbles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">얽어매려 한다면 물거품이 되어버리면 좋을 텐데</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">S&apos;accroche à moi il ferait mieux de se transformer en bulles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si se aferra a mí ojalá se convirtiera en burbujas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sich an mich klammert sollte er sich doch in Luftblasen auflösen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se for para se agarrar em mim seria bom que se transformasse em bolhas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если оно цепляется то пусть бы лучше обратилось в пену</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se mi si avvinghia addosso vorrei solo che si trasformasse in bolle</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Matowaritsuku naraba kihou to kaseba ii no ni</span></p><p begin="1:58.760" end="2:01.260" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:58.760" end="1:59.020">消</span><span begin="1:59.020" end="1:59.240">え</span><span begin="1:59.240" end="1:59.470">て</span><span begin="1:59.470" end="1:59.690">し</span><span begin="1:59.690" end="1:59.910">ま</span><span begin="1:59.910" end="2:00.130">え</span><span begin="2:00.130" end="2:00.350">ば</span><span begin="2:00.350" end="2:00.580">良</span><span begin="2:00.580" end="2:00.820">い</span><span begin="2:00.820" end="2:01.050">の</span><span begin="2:01.050" end="2:01.260">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">不如彻底消散</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">不如徹底消散</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I wish it would just disappear</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사라져 버리면 좋을 텐데</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il ferait mieux de disparaître</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ojalá simplemente desapareciera</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Er sollte einfach verschwinden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Seria bom se simplesmente desaparecesse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пусть бы лучше оно просто исчезло</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Vorrei solo che scomparisse</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kiete shimaeba ii no ni</span></p><p begin="2:12.840" end="2:16.450" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:12.840" end="2:13.340">汚</span><span begin="2:13.340" end="2:13.550">れ</span><span begin="2:13.550" end="2:13.790">な</span><span begin="2:13.790" end="2:14.220">い</span><span begin="2:14.220" end="2:14.460">理</span><span begin="2:14.460" end="2:14.920">想</span><span begin="2:14.920" end="2:15.120">を</span><span begin="2:15.120" end="2:15.670">描</span><span begin="2:15.670" end="2:16.040">く</span><span begin="2:16.040" end="2:16.270">な</span><span begin="2:16.270" end="2:16.450">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">若要描绘无垢理想</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">若要描繪無垢理想</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If painting an unsullied ideal</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">더럽혀지지 않는 이상을 그린다면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Si je dois dessiner un idéal sans tache</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si dibujo un ideal inmaculado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn man ein unbeflecktes Ideal zeichnet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se for para desenhar um ideal imaculado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если рисую незапятнанный идеал</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se disegno un ideale immacolato</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kegarenai risou o egaku nara</span></p><p begin="2:16.630" end="2:20.360" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:16.630" end="2:17.160">全</span><span begin="2:17.160" end="2:17.420">て</span><span begin="2:17.420" end="2:17.740">の</span><span begin="2:17.740" end="2:18.310">存</span><span begin="2:18.310" end="2:18.780">在</span><span begin="2:18.780" end="2:19.010">は</span><span begin="2:19.010" end="2:19.880">瞞</span><span begin="2:19.880" end="2:20.360">し</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">便欺瞒一切存在</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">便欺瞞一切存在</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">All existence is a deception</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">모든 존재는 속임수</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Toutes les existences sont des tromperies</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Toda existencia es un engaño</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ist jede Existenz eine Täuschung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Toda existência é um engano</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Всё существование это обман</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tutte le esistenze sono un inganno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Subete no sonzai wa mayakashi</span></p><p begin="2:20.770" end="2:23.750" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:20.770" end="2:21.390">今</span><span begin="2:21.390" end="2:21.440">、</span><span begin="2:21.440" end="2:21.730">触</span><span begin="2:21.730" end="2:21.960">れ</span><span begin="2:21.960" end="2:22.140">る</span><span begin="2:22.140" end="2:22.600">空</span><span begin="2:22.600" end="2:23.260">想</span><span begin="2:23.260" end="2:23.550">か</span><span begin="2:23.550" end="2:23.750">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">此刻触碰的妄念中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">此刻觸碰的妄念中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Now from the fantasy I touch</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">지금, 닿은 공상에서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">De cette fantaisie que je touche maintenant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ahora, desde esta fantasía que toco</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Aus der Fantasie die ich jetzt berühre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Agora, da fantasia que toco</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сейчас из фантазии к которой прикасаюсь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ora dalla fantasia che tocco</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ima, fureru kuusou kara</span></p><p begin="2:23.980" end="2:28.040" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:23.980" end="2:24.230">こ</span><span begin="2:24.230" end="2:24.450">の</span><span begin="2:24.450" end="2:25.140">声</span><span begin="2:25.140" end="2:25.360">は</span><span begin="2:25.360" end="2:26.280">迸</span><span begin="2:26.280" end="2:28.040">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">迸发出这声线</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">迸發出這聲線</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">This voice surges forth</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 목소리는 솟구쳐 올라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Cette voix jaillit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Brota esta voz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bricht diese Stimme hervor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Esta voz jorra</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Вырывается этот голос</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sgorga questa voce</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kono koe wa hotobashiru</span></p><p begin="2:29.870" end="2:35.640" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:29.870" end="2:30.260">あ</span><span begin="2:30.260" end="2:30.310">、</span><span begin="2:30.570" end="2:30.770">呼</span><span begin="2:30.770" end="2:31.490">吸</span><span begin="2:31.490" end="2:31.730">が</span><span begin="2:31.730" end="2:32.030">で</span><span begin="2:32.030" end="2:32.410">き</span><span begin="2:32.410" end="2:32.640">な</span><span begin="2:32.640" end="2:32.950">い</span><span begin="2:32.950" end="2:33.320">ま</span><span begin="2:33.320" end="2:33.550">ま</span><span begin="2:33.550" end="2:34.260">抱</span><span begin="2:34.260" end="2:34.460">え</span><span begin="2:34.460" end="2:34.790">た</span><span begin="2:34.790" end="2:35.370">痛</span><span begin="2:35.370" end="2:35.640">み</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 无法呼吸却紧拥的痛楚</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 無法呼吸卻緊擁的痛楚</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah the pain embraced while unable to breathe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아, 숨도 쉬지 못한 채 끌어안은 아픔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah la douleur que j&apos;ai portée sans pouvoir respirer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah, este dolor que abrazo sin poder respirar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah der Schmerz den ich atemlos ertrug</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah, a dor que carrego sem conseguir respirar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ах боль что я таила задыхаясь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah il dolore che ho abbracciato senza poter respirare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">A, kokyuu ga dekinai mama kakaeta itami</span></p><p begin="2:36.490" end="2:43.890" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:36.490" end="2:37.170">永</span><span begin="2:37.170" end="2:37.840">遠</span><span begin="2:37.840" end="2:38.040">に</span><span begin="2:38.040" end="2:38.370">咲</span><span begin="2:38.370" end="2:38.700">き</span><span begin="2:38.700" end="2:39.360">誇</span><span begin="2:39.360" end="2:39.650">る</span><span begin="2:39.650" end="2:40.190">造</span><span begin="2:40.190" end="2:40.590">花</span><span begin="2:40.590" end="2:40.810">の</span><span begin="2:40.810" end="2:42.150">様</span><span begin="2:42.640" end="2:43.890">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">如永恒盛放的人造花</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">如永恆盛放的人造花</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Like artificial flowers blooming proudly for eternity</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">영원토록 흐드러지게 피는 조화처럼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Telle une fleur artificielle qui s&apos;épanouit fièrement pour l&apos;éternité</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Como flores artificiales que florecen con orgullo eternamente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wie künstliche Blumen die ewig in voller Pracht blühen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como uma flor artificial que floresce eternamente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Словно искусственный цветок вечно цветущий во всём великолепии</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Come un fiore artificiale che sboccia fiero per l&apos;eternità</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Eien ni sakihokoru zouka no you ni</span></p><p begin="2:44.450" end="2:50.270" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:44.450" end="2:44.910">あ</span><span begin="2:44.910" end="2:44.960">、</span><span begin="2:45.110" end="2:45.700">必</span><span begin="2:45.700" end="2:46.280">然</span><span begin="2:46.280" end="2:46.560">と</span><span begin="2:46.560" end="2:46.940">し</span><span begin="2:46.940" end="2:47.190">て</span><span begin="2:47.190" end="2:47.500">混</span><span begin="2:47.500" end="2:47.860">ざ</span><span begin="2:47.860" end="2:48.090">り</span><span begin="2:48.090" end="2:48.400">合</span><span begin="2:48.400" end="2:48.720">う</span><span begin="2:48.720" end="2:49.010">こ</span><span begin="2:49.010" end="2:49.330">の</span><span begin="2:49.330" end="2:49.900">色</span><span begin="2:49.900" end="2:50.270">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 必然交融的色彩</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 必然交融的色彩</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah this color that inevitably mixes together</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아, 필연적으로 뒤섞이는 이 색이</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah cette couleur qui se mélange comme une fatalité</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah, este color que se mezcla como una inevitabilidad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah diese Farbe die sich unweigerlich vermischt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah, esta cor que se mistura como algo inevitável</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ах этот цвет что неизбежно смешивается</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah questo colore che si mescola come inevitabile</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">A, hitsuzen to shite mazariau kono iro ga</span></p><p begin="2:51.040" end="2:55.600" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:51.040" end="2:51.680">鮮</span><span begin="2:51.680" end="2:52.020">や</span><span begin="2:52.020" end="2:52.350">か</span><span begin="2:52.350" end="2:52.640">な</span><span begin="2:52.640" end="2:52.910">モ</span><span begin="2:52.910" end="2:53.270">ノ</span><span begin="2:53.270" end="2:53.540">ク</span><span begin="2:53.540" end="2:53.880">ロ</span><span begin="2:53.880" end="2:54.150">に</span><span begin="2:54.150" end="2:54.460">染</span><span begin="2:54.460" end="2:54.650">ま</span><span begin="2:54.650" end="2:54.810">っ</span><span begin="2:54.810" end="2:55.240">て</span><span begin="2:55.240" end="2:55.340">い</span><span begin="2:55.340" end="2:55.600">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">正沉入绚烂黑白</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">正沉入絢爛黑白</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is being dyed in a vivid monochrome</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">선명한 흑백으로 물들어 가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Se teint d&apos;un monochrome éclatant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Se va tiñendo de un vívido monocromo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Färbt sich in ein lebhaftes Monochrom</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vai se tingindo de um monocromático vívido</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Окрашивается в яркий монохром</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Si tinge di un vivido bianco e nero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Azayaka na monokuro ni somatte iku</span></p><p begin="2:58.530" end="3:01.940" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:58.530" end="2:59.000">仇</span><span begin="2:59.000" end="2:59.690">花</span><span begin="2:59.690" end="3:00.350">は</span><span begin="3:00.350" end="3:01.050">心</span><span begin="3:01.050" end="3:01.260">の</span><span begin="3:01.260" end="3:01.740">奥</span><span begin="3:01.740" end="3:01.940">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">怨念之花深藏心底</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">怨念之花深藏心底</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A barren flower deep in my heart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">헛된 꽃은 마음속 깊은 곳에</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La fleur stérile au fond de mon cœur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La flor estéril en el fondo de mi corazón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Scheinblüte tief im Herzen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A flor estéril no fundo do coração</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пустоцвет в глубине сердца</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Un fiore sterile nel profondo del cuore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Adabana wa kokoro no oku ni</span></p><p begin="3:02.170" end="3:05.540" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:02.170" end="3:02.380">気</span><span begin="3:02.380" end="3:02.630">付</span><span begin="3:02.630" end="3:02.940">か</span><span begin="3:02.940" end="3:03.320">れ</span><span begin="3:03.320" end="3:03.500">て</span><span begin="3:03.500" end="3:04.230">終</span><span begin="3:04.230" end="3:04.450">わ</span><span begin="3:04.450" end="3:04.790">な</span><span begin="3:04.790" end="3:05.140">い</span><span begin="3:05.140" end="3:05.250">よ</span><span begin="3:05.250" end="3:05.360">う</span><span begin="3:05.360" end="3:05.540">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">唯恐被窥见而凋零</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">唯恐被窺見而凋零</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">So that it won&apos;t end by being noticed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">들켜서 끝나버리지 않도록</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pour ne pas qu&apos;on la remarque et qu&apos;elle prenne fin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Para que no acabe al ser descubierta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Damit sie nicht entdeckt wird und endet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Para que não acabe sendo notada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Чтобы всё не кончилось если его заметят</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Affinché non finisca venendo scoperto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kizukarete shimawanai you ni</span></p><p begin="3:05.810" end="3:12.540" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:05.810" end="3:06.280">誰</span><span begin="3:06.280" end="3:06.740">よ</span><span begin="3:06.740" end="3:07.190">り</span><span begin="3:07.190" end="3:07.550">も</span><span begin="3:07.550" end="3:08.090">純</span><span begin="3:08.090" end="3:08.530">白</span><span begin="3:08.530" end="3:08.750">で</span><span begin="3:08.750" end="3:08.990">あ</span><span begin="3:08.990" end="3:09.170">り</span><span begin="3:09.170" end="3:09.220">、</span><span begin="3:09.450" end="3:10.270">美</span><span begin="3:10.270" end="3:10.760">し</span><span begin="3:10.760" end="3:11.250">く</span><span begin="3:11.250" end="3:11.670">あ</span><span begin="3:11.670" end="3:12.540">れ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">愿比万物更纯白 更绮丽</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">願比萬物更純白 更綺麗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Be more pure white, and beautiful than anyone else</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">누구보다도 순백하며, 아름답기를</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Sois immaculée et plus belle que quiconque</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sé más pura y blanca que nadie, y sé hermosa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sei reinweißer und schöner als jeder andere</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que eu seja mais puramente branca do que ninguém, e bela</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Будь белоснежнее и прекраснее всех</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sii più candida di chiunque altro e sii bella</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dare yori mo junpaku de ari, utsukushiku are</span></p></div></body></tt>